oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Time to Sing Souvenir Ticket
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Offset printing; Williams, Hank, Jr., 1949-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet containing a souvenir ticket for the world premiere of A Time to Sing, featuring Hank Williams, Jr., Shelley Fabares, and Ed Begley, at the Paramount Theatre on August 15. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
